A bird's-eye view of the Wenchang-Qionghai expressway in South China's Hainan Province that will start transportation on Sunday. The 65.7-kilometer expressway will shorten the commuting time from Wenchang town to Boao town to half hour. The new project broke ground in November 2016 links the G9812 Haikou-Wenchang expressway and G98 Hainan Island Ring expressway. Photo: IC Â  
